  <entry>
    <title>Hexo 博客搭建</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</id>
    <published>2021-02-12T10:25:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-17T20:53:51.842Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><h1 id="Hexo-博客搭建"><a href="#Hexo-博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo 博客搭建"></a>Hexo 博客搭建</h1><blockquote><p>​        Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。Hexo 使用 <a href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/">Markdown</a>（或其他渲染引擎）解析文章，在几秒内，即可利用靓丽的主题生成静态网页。</p><img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/hexo.svg" style="zoom:18%;"><p>​        我们可以轻松的将 Hexo 博客部署在 GitHub Pages 上，不需要再购买云服务器ESC。我通过官方文档以及一些其他资料列举了以下的几个步骤，借此方便在对 Hexo 博客有使用需求时的查询。</p></blockquote><h2 id="一、准备工作"><a href="#一、准备工作" class="headerlink" title="一、准备工作"></a>一、准备工作</h2><h3 id="1-1-安装"><a href="#1-1-安装" class="headerlink" title="1.1    安装"></a>1.1    安装</h3><blockquote><ul><li>管理：<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png"><a href="http://git-scm.com/">Git</a></li><li>环境：<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/nodejs.png"><a href="http://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a>（版本需高于10.13，建议使用12.x版本）</li><li>应用： <img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/hexo.svg" style="zoom:4%;"><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">Hexo</a></li></ul></blockquote><h4 id="1-1-1-安装-Git"><a href="#1-1-1-安装-Git" class="headerlink" title="1.1.1    安装 Git"></a>1.1.1    安装 Git</h4><ol><li><p>依照操作系统安装 <strong>Git</strong>:</p><ul><li>Windows 版本下载地址：<a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">https://git-scm.com/download/win</a></li><li>Mac 版本下载安装程序：<a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/git-osx-installer/">http://sourceforge.net/projects/git-osx-installer/</a></li><li>Linux (Ubuntu, Debian)指令：<code>sudo apt-get install git-core</code></li><li>Linux (Fedora, Red Hat, CentOS)指令：<code>sudo yum install git-core</code></li></ul></li><li><p>使用cmd输入 <code>git --version</code> 检查Git版本：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\admin&gt; git --version</span><br><span class="line">git version 2.30.1.windows.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>完成（更详细的Git使用教程：<a href="https://www.runoob.com/git/git-install-setup.html">Git 安装配置</a>）</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-1-2-安装-Node-js"><a href="#1-1-2-安装-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.1.2    安装 Node.js"></a>1.1.2    安装 Node.js</h4><ol><li><p>通过官网下载安装 <strong>Node.js</strong>：<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/</a></p><ul><li><p>在 <em>LTS (长期支持版 )</em> 中点击 <em>Windows Installer (Windows 安装包 )</em> 下载 Windows 版本的安装包。</p></li><li><p>在 <em>LTS (长期支持版 )</em> 中点击 <em>masOS Installer (masOS 安装包 )</em> 下载 masOS 版本的安装包。</p></li><li><p>Ubuntu指令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install nodejs</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install npm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>使用cmd输入 <code>node --version</code> 检查Node.js版本：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\Nebula&gt; node --version</span><br><span class="line">v15.0.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>完成（更详细的Git使用教程：<a href="https://www.runoob.com/nodejs/nodejs-install-setup.html">Node.js 安装配置</a>）</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-1-3-安装-Hexo"><a href="#1-1-3-安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.1.3    安装 Hexo"></a>1.1.3    安装 Hexo</h4><ol><li><p>打开刚刚安装的<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash</p></li><li><p>输入 <code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code> 安装</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm install -g hexo-cli</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">changed 66 packages, and audited 67 packages in 15s    # 成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入 <code>hexo version</code> 检查版本</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo version</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">hexo: 5.3.0</span><br><span class="line">hexo-cli: 4.2.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-创建网站"><a href="#1-2-创建网站" class="headerlink" title="1.2    创建网站"></a>1.2    创建网站</h3></li></ol><h4 id="1-2-1-创建网站源代码"><a href="#1-2-1-创建网站源代码" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1    创建网站源代码"></a>1.2.1    创建网站源代码</h4><ol><li><p>创建一个空文件夹作为项目文件夹：在 cmd 输入 <code>md E:/Blog</code></p></li><li><p>打开<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash，<strong>移动到项目文件夹</strong>：在 Git 中输入 <code>cd E:/Blog</code></p></li><li><p>新建网站所需要的文件：在 Git 中输入 <code>hexo init</code> 和 <code>npm install</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo init</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Cloning hexo-starter https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-starter.git</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Install dependencies</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start blogging with Hexo!    # 成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm install</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">added 6 packages, and audited 185 packages in 2s    # 成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>完成。项目文件夹的目录为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml# 网站的配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds# 用于建立文件的模板</span><br><span class="line">├── source# 资源文件夹</span><br><span class="line">|   ├── _drafts</span><br><span class="line">|   └── _posts</span><br><span class="line">└── themes# 主题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-2-2-修改网站配置"><a href="#1-2-2-修改网站配置" class="headerlink" title="1.2.2    修改网站配置"></a>1.2.2    修改网站配置</h4></li><li><p>用记事本打开项目文件夹中的 <code>_config.yml</code></p></li><li><p>修改网站的配置</p><table><thead><tr><th><div style="width:100px">参数</div></th><th align="left">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>title</code></td><td align="left">网站标题</td></tr><tr><td><code>subtitle</code></td><td align="left">网站副标题</td></tr><tr><td><code>description</code></td><td align="left">网站描述</td></tr><tr><td><code>keywords</code></td><td align="left">网站的关键词。支援多个关键词。</td></tr><tr><td><code>author</code></td><td align="left">您的名字</td></tr><tr><td><code>language</code></td><td align="left">网站使用的语言。对于简体中文用户来说，使用不同的主题可能需要设置成不同的值，请参考你的主题的文档自行设置，常见的有 <code>zh-Hans</code>和 <code>zh-CN</code>。</td></tr><tr><td><code>timezone</code></td><td align="left">网站时区。Hexo 默认使用您电脑的时区。请参考 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones">时区列表</a> 进行设置，如 <code>America/New_York</code>, <code>Japan</code>, 和 <code>UTC</code> 。一般的，对于中国大陆地区可以使用 <code>Asia/Shanghai</code>。</td></tr></tbody></table><p>实例：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Nebula Nya~ Nya~&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;喵喵喵，星云的资料小屋&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;介绍，在网站中看不到，只能在源代码（F12）中看到&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">learning</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Nebula</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;zh-CN&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改网址设置</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">参数</th><th align="left">描述</th><th align="left">默认值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><code>url</code></td><td align="left">网址, must starts with <code>http://</code> or <code>https://</code></td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>root</code></td><td align="left">网站根目录</td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>permalink</code></td><td align="left">文章的 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/permalinks">永久链接</a> 格式</td><td align="left"><code>:year/:month/:day/:title/</code></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>permalink_defaults</code></td><td align="left">永久链接中各部分的默认值</td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>pretty_urls</code></td><td align="left">改写 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/variables"><code>permalink</code></a> 的值来美化 URL</td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>pretty_urls.trailing_index</code></td><td align="left">是否在永久链接中保留尾部的 <code>index.html</code>，设置为 <code>false</code> 时去除</td><td align="left"><code>true</code></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><code>pretty_urls.trailing_html</code></td><td align="left">是否在永久链接中保留尾部的 <code>.html</code>, 设置为 <code>false</code> 时去除 (<em>对尾部的 <code>index.html</code>无效</em>)</td><td align="left"><code>true</code></td></tr></tbody></table><p>实例：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 如果网站是从子目录开始，将 url 设置为 &#x27;http://example.com/child&#x27; </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 并且将 root 设置为 &#x27;/child&#x27;，这里的child应替换为子目录的目录名。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">http://example.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">root:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">:title/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink_defaults:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">pretty_urls:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">trailing_index:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">trailing_html:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>找到 <code>post_asset_folder</code> 修改为 <code>true</code> ，为之后在文章中添加图片创建资源文件夹。</p></li><li><p>其他设置暂时不用修改，详情请见：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration">Hexo 配置</a></p></li></ol><h4 id="1-2-3-在本地创建网站"><a href="#1-2-3-在本地创建网站" class="headerlink" title="1.2.3    在本地创建网站"></a>1.2.3    在本地创建网站</h4><ol><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入 <code>hexo g</code> 或 <code>hexo generate</code> 生成静态文件。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo g</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing          # 若这里有警告，可能的原因是使用了高版本的 node.js</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Files loaded in 640 ms    # 可以卸载掉高版本，使用稳定的12版本，例如：12.20</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: archives/2021/index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: index.html</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Generated: js/script.js</span><br><span class="line">·</span><br><span class="line">·  # 这里是生成静态文件 </span><br><span class="line">·</span><br><span class="line">INFO  17 files generated in 1.9 s    # 成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png" alt="image-20210210161054123">Git Bash 中输入 <code>hexo s</code> 或 <code>hexo server</code> 启动服务器。默认情况下，访问网址为： <code>http://localhost:4000/</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo s</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Start processing    # 成功</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：允许使用网络；保证运行这条命令时<strong>在网站项目文件夹路径下</strong>。</p></li><li><p>在浏览器中打开网址 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> ，就可以看到网站了。</p></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中使用快捷键 <code>Ctrl + C</code> 停止。</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-2-4-更换网站主题"><a href="#1-2-4-更换网站主题" class="headerlink" title="1.2.4    更换网站主题"></a>1.2.4    更换网站主题</h4><blockquote><p>这里仅用一个主题作为示范，可以到 <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">Hexo 主题</a> 浏览更多主题。</p><p>在 <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">Hexo 主题</a> 里，点击主题的图片进入样例网站；点击主题的名字进入github项目页面，可以在其中查看介绍和使用说明。</p></blockquote><ol><li><p>选择一个主题，这里选择Purely主题：<a href="https://github.com/geekrainy/hexo-theme-purely">https://github.com/geekrainy/hexo-theme-purely</a></p></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入<code>git clone https://github.com/geekrainy/hexo-theme-purely.git themes/purely</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/geekrainy/hexo-theme-purely.git themes/purely</span></span><br><span class="line">Cloning into &#x27;themes/purely&#x27;...</span><br><span class="line">remote: Enumerating objects: 801, done.</span><br><span class="line">remote: Total 801 (delta 0), reused 0 (delta 0), pack-reused 801</span><br><span class="line">Receiving objects: 100% (801/801), 2.46 MiB | 423.00 KiB/s, done.</span><br><span class="line">Resolving deltas: 100% (355/355), done.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在**项目文件夹(./)**中修改 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件。找到 <code>theme</code> 修改为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: purely</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在**主题文件夹(./theme/purely)**中修改 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，也可以不修改。详情可见：<a href="https://github.com/geekrainy/hexo-theme-purely">主题介绍</a></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 主菜单栏</span></span><br><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: /</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives</span><br><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 模式</span></span><br><span class="line">color: blue</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 文本</span></span><br><span class="line">excerpt_link: Read More</span><br><span class="line">fancybox: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 图标</span></span><br><span class="line">favicon: /favicon.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-2-5-发布文章"><a href="#1-2-5-发布文章" class="headerlink" title="1.2.5    发布文章"></a>1.2.5    发布文章</h4></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入 <code>hexo new &quot;文章名&quot;</code> 在 <code>./source/_posts</code> 创建一个 markdown文本文件。</p></li><li><p>使用markdown编辑器（例如：<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/typora.png">Typora）编写文件并保存。</p></li><li><p>刷新页面。文章是即时刷新的，所以不用重启服务器。</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-2-6-为文章添加图片"><a href="#1-2-6-为文章添加图片" class="headerlink" title="1.2.6    为文章添加图片"></a>1.2.6    为文章添加图片</h4><ol><li><p>确保网站配置中 <code>post_asset_folder</code> 为 <code>true</code> ，在使用 <code>hexo new</code> 时会创建一个与文章同名的文件夹。</p></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入 <code>npm install hexo-asset-image --save</code> 安装上传图片插件。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">added 21 packages, and audited 210 packages in 4s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>将图片存到这个与文章同名的文件夹。</p></li><li><p>在markdown文章中，图片使用相对路径。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── source</span><br><span class="line">    └── _posts</span><br><span class="line">        ├── 文章.md# markdown文件</span><br><span class="line">        └── 文章# 同名文件夹</span><br><span class="line">            └── image1.png</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">文章.md：</span><br><span class="line">这里是图片：![image](image1.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li></ol><h3 id="1-3-将-Hexo-部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#1-3-将-Hexo-部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="1.3    将 Hexo 部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>1.3    将 Hexo 部署到 GitHub Pages</h3><h4 id="1-3-1-在-GitHub-创建-repository（仓库）"><a href="#1-3-1-在-GitHub-创建-repository（仓库）" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1    在 GitHub 创建 repository（仓库）"></a>1.3.1    在 GitHub 创建 repository（仓库）</h4><blockquote><p>这个仓库用来存储生成好的静态网站</p><p>要保证 repository 的名字为你的 GitHub 的账号加.github.io</p></blockquote><ol><li><p>登录或注册 GitHub 账户。</p></li><li><p>创建仓库：</p><ol><li><p>点击 GitHub 页面的右上角用户头像左边的加号中的 “New repository” ；</p></li><li><p>在 “Repository name” 中填入你的账号名加.github.io；</p><p><img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20210216161027786.png" alt="例：你的 GitHub 的账号加.github.io"></p></li><li><p>点击 “Create repository” 创建仓库。</p></li></ol><p>注：仓库创建不会立即完成需要等待一段时间（通常不会超过30分钟）。</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-3-2-配置-SSH-Key"><a href="#1-3-2-配置-SSH-Key" class="headerlink" title="1.3.2    配置 SSH Key"></a>1.3.2    配置 SSH Key</h4><ol><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入以下命令设置用户名和邮箱名：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入 <code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的邮箱&quot;</code> ，一直回车（3次），生成SSH Key：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 1017570673@qq.com</span></span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/c/Users/Nebula/.ssh/id_rsa):# 这里按回车</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):# 这里按回车</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:# 这里按回车</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /c/Users/Nebula/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /c/Users/Nebula/.ssh/id_rsa.pub# 公钥的位置</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">The key&#x27;s randomart image is:# SSH Key 的指纹</span><br><span class="line">+---[RSA 3072]----+</span><br><span class="line">|  =.o            |</span><br><span class="line">| . B             |</span><br><span class="line">|  + o o          |</span><br><span class="line">|.. o + .         |</span><br><span class="line">|+.. o . S        |</span><br><span class="line">|o=oB.+           |</span><br><span class="line">|=oO+*.   E       |</span><br><span class="line">|o===*o  o        |</span><br><span class="line">|++o==B+.         |</span><br><span class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>从上面找到公钥位置 <code>C:\Users\Nebula\.ssh\</code> ，打开方式选择用记事本打开 <code>id_rsa.pub</code> ，复制其中内容</p></li><li><p>打开 GitHub 点击右上角用户头像中的 “Settings”，点击 “SSH and GPG Keys”，再点击 “New SSH key”</p></li><li><p>将从 <code>id_rsa.pub</code> 复制的内容粘贴到 “Key”，任取一个名字填到”Title”中，点击 “Add SSH key”。</p></li></ol><h4 id="1-3-3-修改配置文件与部署"><a href="#1-3-3-修改配置文件与部署" class="headerlink" title="1.3.3    修改配置文件与部署"></a>1.3.3    修改配置文件与部署</h4><ol><li><p>在项目文件夹中修改 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件。找到 <code>deploy</code> 修改为：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/你的账号名/你的账号名.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装 <code>hexo-deploy-git</code> ：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在<img src="/Hexo-%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/git.png">Git Bash 中输入以下命令部署到 GitHub：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate# 生成静态网站</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy# 部署</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
